# Strict Rules
- **Tech Stack:** pnpm, TypeScript (strict mode), Tailwind CSS, GraphQL (Apollo Client)
- **Linting:** Use ESLint + Prettier. Prefer functional components and Arrow functions.
- **Styling:** Utility-first Tailwind only. No CSS files unless necessary. Ensure all components are fully responsive using a mobile-first approach.
- **Data:** Use https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/ as the REST source, but wrap it in a GraphQL schema.
- **State Management:** Use Redux Toolkit (RTK) to manage local state for added reviews.